Support email: lessontrackerforios@gmail.com

How to add a student: On the welcome page click the person button on the top right to see all current students and add new ones.

How to add lessons: Open the side menu after selecting a pupil to add lessons and also see the pupil summary support.

Deleting pupils/lessons: Swipe on the pupil/lesson to delete.

Mail: Press to mail button next to the lesson to send an email of the lesson details to the pupil.*

*Apple's Mail app has to be installed to use the mail feature.

